</div>
<div class="video-examples-featured">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="iuqrku" data-video-descrip="As befits the Goddess of Darkness, she attacks mainly with petrifying beams or blasts of concentrated darkness." data-video-title="Medusa" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/iuqrku_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/iuqrku.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/CastingAShadow" data-video-tropename="Casting a Shadow" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="4.00" data-video-rating-count="3" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/KidIcarusUprising" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link featured-widget-vid">
<div class="featured-widget-vid-iframe">
<video id='featured-video-player' class='video-js vjs-default-skin vjs-16-9' controls data-setup='{"ga": {"eventsToTrack": ["error"]}}'>
</video>
</div>
</a>
<h2 class="bold font-l">Medusa</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
As befits the Goddess of Darkness, she attacks mainly with petrifying beams or blasts of concentrated darkness. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="7zgm2q" data-video-descrip="In &amp;quot;Oogie's Revenge&amp;quot;, Oogie Boogie has the ability to send his shadow to do his bidding. " data-video-title="Oogie Boogie" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/7zgm2q_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/shadow_oogie_boogie_of_the_nightmare_before_christmas_oogies_revenge_boses.png" data-video-trope="Main/CastingAShadow" data-video-tropename="Casting a Shadow" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/TheNightmareBeforeChristmasOogiesRevenge" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/shadow_oogie_boogie_of_the_nightmare_before_christmas_oogies_revenge_boses.png">
<p><span class="bold">Oogie Boogie</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="vl5lpa" data-video-descrip="As Darkness Dragoon, Rose has the power to transform and wield the elemental magic of darkness in battle." data-video-title="Rose" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/vl5lpa_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/vl5lpa.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/CastingAShadow" data-video-tropename="Casting a Shadow" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/LegendOfDragoon" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/vl5lpa.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Rose</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="zk722n" data-video-descrip="As ruler of the Land of Shadow, the Dark Queen has the power to vomit up living shadows to do her bidding." data-video-title="The Dark Queen" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/zk722n_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/zk722n.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/CastingAShadow" data-video-tropename="Casting a Shadow" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Film/Mirrormask" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/zk722n.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">The Dark Queen</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="qi33nb" data-video-descrip="One of his powers can darken the room as you battle." data-video-title="Arlon the Serene" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/qi33nb_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/qi33nb.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/CastingAShadow" data-video-tropename="Casting a Shadow" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/KidIcarusUprising" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/qi33nb.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Arlon the Serene</span></p>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
